---
title: Spicy Burmese Red Pork Bowl with Green Onion Jasmine Rice
description: Inspired by the flavours of Myanmar, this red pork stir-fry usually takes all day to make, but we've swapped out pork shoulder for fast frying ham. Its red colour comes from a quick caramel sauce mixed with soy and sriracha. This dish packs a punch of flavour from across the globe!
